# EPC drawings are NOT published.
#
# publish/ is the GitHub Pages root (CNAME -> tendrara.neo-ware.com), so anything
# committed here is served anonymously on the public internet. The 90 ESA/ITALFLUID
# PDFs were being served that way — they now live in the PRIVATE Supabase Storage
# bucket `plant-docs` and are reached through signed URLs (doc-url Edge Function),
# which require a signed-in session.
#
# Do not remove this rule. If you need a drawing on the site, it belongs in storage
# and gets linked from the E&I Navigator (EI70 / EI80), not committed here.
docs/

